92
00:05:33,482 --> 00:05:36,302
that all are tungsten-based.

93
00:05:36,302 --> 00:05:40,337
And with these materials,
we never go above that level,

94
00:05:40,337 --> 00:05:45,013
even if we have 25,000 discharges
